Participants 53 155 6
The efficacy of metronidazole and tinidazole has been compared in 31 patients with hepatic amoebiasis.
Participants 337 580 6
15 patients received metronidazole and 16 tinidazole, in random order. The 2 groups were comparable. Both drugs were given orally in a single daily dose of 2g for a minimum of 3 days, with treatment extended if considered clinically advisable.
